							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="310v" to="411v"/>
								<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Hafṭarot</title>
								<note>
									<p>Imperfect at the end.</p>
									<p>Hafṭarot are preceded by two illuminated pages, <locus n="306v, 307r"/>, and the bededictions to say before and after the reading of the Hafṭarah, <locus from="309v" to="310r"/>, written c16th century, provided with superlinear punctuation.</p>
								</note>
							</msItem>
